{"type":"message","id":"0969caa0","parentId":"b987198e","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:24:41.771Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both session-summary and bootstrap hooks are registered and ready. The issue is that there are no session-summary files in memory/. This could mean:\n1. The session-summary hook isn't generating files (maybe the session didn't end properly)\n2. Or the files were cleaned up\n\nLet me check if there's a recent session file.","thinkingSignature":"399c2104de6832853ace4098f49c7804ec925980bd416e3d49571e4516deb9ca"},{"type":"text","text":"链路是通的，但有个问题：没有 session-summary 文件生成。\n\n- ✅ `session-summary` hook：已注册，状态 ready\n- ✅ `bootstrap` hook（extra-files）：已注册，状态 ready\n\n两个 hook 都在跑，但 `memory/` 下找不到 `*-session-summary.md`。可能原因：\n\n1. 昨天的 session 没有通过 `/new` 或 `/reset` 结束（直接关窗口就没触发）\n2. 或者 summary 被 `pruneOldSummaries()` 清理了（30 天过期，但刚建的不应该）\n\n要不要我手动跑一次 `session-summary` hook 的逻辑，看看能不能生成一个测试摘要？或者你直接 `/new` 开新 session 就能验证注入了。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3470,"output":213,"cacheRead":19750,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23433,"cost":{"input":0.001041,"output":0.0002556,"cacheRead":0.0011849999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0024815999999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776173071402,"responseId":"062d730f31932a201c6f178637c2ecf0"}}
